===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|flock||flock|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|flocc||flock, company, troop|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*flukkaz}}, {{m|gem-pro|*flakka-||crowd, troop}}. Cognate with {{etyl|gml|-}} {{term|vlocke||crowd, flock|lang=gml}}, {{etyl|non|-}} {{term|flokkr||crowd, troop, band, flock|lang=non}}. Perhaps related to {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|folc||crowd, troop, band|lang=ang}}. More at {{l|en|folk}}.

